data.description: Freshly constructed house with 3 bedrooms and a den. The floor plan incorporates a modern kitchen with pristine cabinets and quartz, a cleverly concealed laundry and a spacious living/dining area. The generously proportioned interior flows effortlessly from the open-plan living space to the lanai from which you can admire the views of the garden and beyond. This stylish residence is nestled on a corner lot. Secured with a smart lock. Disclaimer: Some of the photos are virtually staged.
